{"id": "1516785386657939487", "channel_id": "1510911214346305566", "type": 0, "author_id": "1425265631078645841", "author_name": "megane0965_78083", "author_bot": false, "content": "幻夢カエクス\n18ターン\nタイスキー、超次元倉庫、念動力をやりくりしてニム3コスを打ちまくるのが楽しい。\n黒章1円足りなくて甘いインクを買えなかったのが致命的だった。", "timestamp": "2026-06-17T12:43:36.689000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1516785385727070358", "filename": "IMG_8411.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 607509, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1510911214346305566/1516785385727070358/IMG_8411.png?ex=6a33e7f8&is=6a329678&hm=09fa08c356efed534d4a25131f91aad1d39b3e6e6c26e984e99dc1517085f0c4&"}, {"id": "1516785386238513152", "filename": "IMG_8410.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 385302, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1510911214346305566/1516785386238513152/IMG_8410.png?ex=6a33e7f8&is=6a329678&hm=2544beacd020fd60af0ffe2640b800654aa018aca90ecc5115e0d5d10a9da243&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510911214346305566", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "ニムフィーアの毒パ研究日誌", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1516603359094767667", "channel_id": "1458760640351965361", "type": 0, "author_id": "1064544224579694672", "author_name": "suzuri9701", "author_bot": false, "content": "エルトン船長、マーフィーに対してこのガキが…あんまりふざけてると海に放り投げるぞ……みたいな反応してたけど、内心では彼女が苦難の道を歩むきっかけの一因になってしまったことにしっかり負い目を感じてて、良い😄", "timestamp": "2026-06-17T00:40:17.936000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458760640351965361", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "つぶやき", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1516604037716377710", "channel_id": "1458760640351965361", "type": 0, "author_id": "1064544224579694672", "author_name": "suzuri9701", "author_bot": false, "content": "エルトン・シレスト・マーフィーの三人の関係割と萌……なんだけど\n深夜帯に三人で蒸しプリンとかを作る回が見たい(いきなり幻覚の話⁉️)", "timestamp": "2026-06-17T00:42:59.732000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍮", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458760640351965361", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "つぶやき", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1516605300721975356", "channel_id": "1458760640351965361", "type": 0, "author_id": "1064544224579694672", "author_name": "suzuri9701", "author_bot": false, "content": "忘却前夜の時代観があまり分かりきれてないんだけど、\nソナニール号って船の規模的にも基本的に長期間の航海前提ぽそうだから、甘味とか嗜好品ってすごく限られてそうだなって思ってて……嗜好品とかでお酒とか出されてもマーフィーって飲めない…と思うし\n甘味の類も基本的にドライフルーツとかなんじゃないかなって思っており\nどっかの港に停泊した日に生もの系のものとかを作る回とか、見たい(…❓)", "timestamp": "2026-06-17T00:48:00.856000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-17T00:48:30.481000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458760640351965361", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "つぶやき", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1516606139650019489", "channel_id": "1458760640351965361", "type": 0, "author_id": "1064544224579694672", "author_name": "suzuri9701", "author_bot": false, "content": "えっマーフィーって飲めるのかな❓実際に起きてるときに経験してる時間の感覚だと成年してるイメージないけど、本来の年齢的にはガッツリ成人よね", "timestamp": "2026-06-17T00:51:20.872000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458760640351965361", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "つぶやき", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1516608912957243412", "channel_id": "1458760640351965361", "type": 0, "author_id": "1064544224579694672", "author_name": "suzuri9701", "author_bot": false, "content": "あとめちゃくちゃ話変わるしお知らせにも書いてある話なんですけど、6/10のアプデで遺物関連に沙耶イベの固有遺物も登録されるようになってるので……\nイベ全部終わってる人でも登録できてない人は各自でステージ入る必要ありますね(クリア自体はしなくても大丈夫)", "timestamp": "2026-06-17T01:02:22.080000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1516608912663515206", "filename": "IMG_5848.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 834449, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1458760640351965361/1516608912663515206/IMG_5848.png?ex=6a33ec5e&is=6a329ade&hm=86f632d9866e5930bfb8ecc166b8e71c60e39cfa7376f945f63024a010c96b9d&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458760640351965361", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "つぶやき", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1516609366055325899", "channel_id": "1458760640351965361", "type": 0, "author_id": "1064544224579694672", "author_name": "suzuri9701", "author_bot": false, "content": "蓄音機とかはイベ終わってもストーリー自体は常設だろうと思うから解放できるけど\n遺物はイベ復刻来ないと解放できないよねたしか(事件マスも該当イベ来ないと開けられないのあるし)\nまぁ沙耶イベ自体は期間長めだけど", "timestamp": "2026-06-17T01:04:10.107000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👀", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1458760640351965361", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "つぶやき", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
